{"id": 1098, "genre": 1000, "title": "Kindle对你的阅读习惯有什么影响？", "description": "别告诉我你买Kindle是用来盖泡面的就行。（题图来自：Thomas Hedger）", "record_count": 5912, "comment_count": 38, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160721141317PWtqIdSM2vfX5ZwO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-21T17:00:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 979, "title": "Kindle对你的阅读习惯有什么影响？", "content": "Kindle对你的阅读习惯有什么影响？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 95718, "content": "有电子版的书，再也不会买纸质版", "image": "img/option/option/20160706143255lQRuCLdMVSnTgiOZ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95719, "content": "有的时候一本书没有电子版，就懒得买了", "image": "img/option/option/20160706143321Ik4N3biS1Fr98ulh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95721, "content": "因为购买方便，看了很多之前不会买的畅销书和小说", "image": "img/option/option/201607061457248ieXRbuYvrxmpjSO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95731, "content": "订了Kindle Unlimited后，看了更多之前不会看的书", "image": "img/option/option/201607061548008EI9tGo0JMyiRBOT.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95732, "content": "屯了一堆下载之后再也不会打开的免费文档", "image": "img/option/option/20160706153250Isx3K8S1cOM5EgZj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95733, "content": "时不常刷一下今日特价，买了好些八毛一块的", "image": "img/option/option/20160706153323lsuUow6gKCQVN1pG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95734, "content": "习惯了利用边边角角的时间看书", "image": "img/option/option/20160706153346NESzsGLA0yBHhDdZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 95735, "content": "我没什么改变，倒是Kindle在角落里吃灰", "image": "img/option/option/20160706155446ylbvAuheG64FUr5i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}